OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784722710
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to falsifying MOT on
OL,4,CSt Mellons crash car
OL,6,FA garage mechanic has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto fraud after falsely issuing an MOT
OL,8,Fcertificate for a car later involved
OL,9,Fin a crash that killed three people.
OL,11,FNeil Lewis, 47, from Ely in Cardiff,
OL,12,Fadmitted fraud by dishonest
OL,13,Frepresentation at Cardiff Magistrate's
OL,14,FCourt on Tuesday (21 July).
OL,16,FThe court heard how the car - a
OL,17,FVolkswagen Tiguan - had been badly
OL,18,Fdamaged after being involved in a
OL,19,Fcrash in Scotland on 15 December 2021,
OL,20,Fwith its airbag system still deployed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
