PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784722710
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to falsifying MOT on
OL,4,CSt Mellons crash car
OL,6,FIt was later salvaged and sold at
OL,7,Fauction, where it was bought by Joel
OL,8,FLia, from Cardiff.
OL,10,FNo repair work had been carried out on
OL,11,Fthe vehicle at this point and Mr Lia
OL,12,Fgave it to Neil Lewis to carry out an
OL,13,FMOT and repair work.
OL,15,FThe car failed its MOT on 9 February
OL,16,F2023, with problems with its
OL,17,Fseatbelts, and a warning light
OL,18,Findicating problems with the seatbelts
OL,19,For airbag system or even both.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,432,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784722710
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to falsifying MOT on
OL,4,CSt Mellons crash car
OL,6,FProsecutor Francesca Parry said Lewis
OL,7,Fpassed the car after a retest with
OL,8,Fsome advisories, and texted Mr Lia to
OL,9,Finform him, adding "you've got to sort
OL,10,Fthe seatbelt and airbag light".
OL,12,FThe court heard that the broken
OL,13,Fseatbelts at the front of the car had
OL,14,Fnot been replaced since the 2021 crash.
OL,16,FIn March 2023, the car was involved in
OL,17,Fa crash that killed Eve Smith and
OL,18,FDarcy Ross, both 21, and Rafel Jeanne,
OL,19,F24,
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
