PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784722710
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to falsifying MOT on
OL,4,CSt Mellons crash car
OL,6,FThey were found dead at the scene of
OL,7,Fthe incident on the A48 in the St
OL,8,FMellons area of Cardiff on 6 March `
OL,9,Falmost 48 hours after they were all
OL,10,Flast seen.
OL,12,FPassengers Sophie Russon, then 20, and
OL,13,FShane Loughlin, then 32, who were
OL,14,Fseriously injured, were also found
OL,15,Fwith the Volkswagen Tiguan they had
OL,16,Fbeen travelling in.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
