OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1784722710
OL,3,CMan pleads guilty to falsifying MOT on
OL,4,CSt Mellons crash car
OL,6,FIn Novermber 2025, the Independent
OL,7,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC)
OL,8,Fconfirmed six police officers are to
OL,9,Fface misconduct proceedings in
OL,10,Frelation to their handling of the
OL,11,Fcrash.
OL,13,FLewis will be sentenced on August 19.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
